3. 模型¶

3.1 首先采用线性回归模型，拟合函数为：¶

$$\hat{y}(w, x)=w_{0}+w_{1} x_{1}+\ldots+w_{p} x_{p}$$

$$ \min _{w}\|X w-y\|_{2}^{2} $$

In [36]:
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression

#

# 
def plot_pred(model, y_test, y_pred, mae, rmse, r2, savepath=None):
    plt.figure(figsize=(20,5))
    plt.grid(axis='x', ls='--')
    ax = plt.gca()
    ax.set_xticks(range(len(y_test)))
    plt.scatter(range(len(y_pred)), y_pred, c='b', label='pred')
    plt.scatter(range(len(y_test.values)), y_test, c='r', label='target')
    plt.legend()
    plt.xlabel('')
    plt.ylabel('')
    plt.title('({}), mae:{:.2f}, rmse:{:.2f}, r2:{:.2f}'.format(type(model).__name__, mae, rmse, r2))
#     plt.savefig(savepath / '{}.png'.format(type(model).__name__))
    plt.show()
    
def plot_pred_scatter(model, y_test, y_pred, mae, rmse, r2, savepath=None):
    fig = plt.figure(figsize=(7,7))
    ax = fig.add_subplot()
    plt.plot(range(400), range(400), 'r--')
    plt.scatter(y_test, y_pred)
    plt.title('{}vs'.format(type(model).__name__))
    plt.xlabel('')
    plt.ylabel('')
    plt.text(0.1, 0.8, s='mae:{:.2f}\nrmse:{:.2f}\nr2:{:.2f}'.format(mae, rmse, r2), transform=ax.transAxes, fontsize=15)
#     plt.savefig(savepath/'{}.png'.format(type(model).__name__))
    plt.show()
    
    
    
def plot_importance(model, colums, savepath=None):
    plt.figure(figsize=(8,4))
    plt.bar(x=colums, height=model.feature_importances_)
    plt.title(' | {}'.format(type(model).__name__))
    plt.xlabel('')
    plt.ylabel('')
#     plt.savefig(savepath/'_{}.png'.format(type(model).__name__))
    plt.show()
    
    
def calc_metrics(y_test, y_pred):
    from sklearn.metrics import mean_absolute_error, mean_squared_error, r2_score
    mae = mean_absolute_error(y_test, y_pred)
    rmse = mean_squared_error(y_test, y_pred, squared=False)
    r2 = r2_score(y_test, y_pred)
    return mae, rmse, r2
